    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it's been my absolute pride and joy, but it\u2019s finally time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It drives like a total dream and is in truly spectacular shape inside and out\u2014not a speck out of place. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
