    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed: the rear subframe is reinforced with Turner plates, the double VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components, and the rod bearings have been replaced with WPC-treated bearings for peace of mind. The individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, providing the immediate, linear throttle response this chassis is known for. No deferred maintenance, no subframe cracks, and no VANOS rattle. This is an investment-grade enthusiast vehicle with a clean oil analysis history and documented service intervals.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_21_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_21",
      "description": "Pristine condition. No mechanical issues. Original paint. Interior like new. Garage kept. Single owner. Title in hand.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true collector-grade example that must be seen to be fully appreciated. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected since day one by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks on the bodywork. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It has been meticulously maintained exclusively at authorized service centers, with a comprehensive binder of service records included in the sale. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Strictly garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a virtually new vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
